task id=1 status=todo {
    title "Initialize project from scaffold"
    created "2026-03-14T17:11:47.551455+00:00"
    modified "2026-04-23T10:20:58.329750+00:00"
    description #"""
Takes a project name and a git remote URL as input.

1. Update README.md: replace scaffold-specific content (clone instructions,
   title, and the `https://scaffold.localhost` URL) with the new project name
2. Update CLAUDE.md: update project overview and swap
   `https://scaffold.localhost` / `https://scaffold-preview.localhost` to use
   the new project name
3. Update `client/index.html`: update `<title>`, `<meta name="description">`,
   and Open Graph meta tags with the new project name and description
4. Update root `package.json` `"name"` with the new project name
   (lowercase/hyphenated)
5. Update `client/package.json`: in the portless-wrapped `dev` and `preview`
   scripts, replace the `scaffold` / `scaffold-preview` route names with the
   new project name (e.g. `portless <name> vite`, `portless <name>-preview
   vite preview`)
6. Update `client/playwright.config.ts`: replace
   `https://scaffold-preview.localhost` with `https://<name>-preview.localhost`
7. `rm -rf .git && git init`
8. `git add -A && git commit -m "Initial commit"`
9. `git remote add origin <url> && git push -u origin main`
"""#
}
